items.title: Arugula New York Steak
items.description: Arugula New York Steak salad is a delicious dish that is new on the menu. This arugula based salad is tossed with beets, sweet cherry tomatoes, and gorgonzola cheese. Thin slices of New York steak is served on top of this bed of deliciousness.

items.title: Butter Fish Filet Green Salad
items.description: Butter Fish Filet Green Salad is a salad tossed with green beans, beets, cherry tomatoes, and served with a side of mashed potato. Hot garlic bread is placed on top of the salad with crispy fish filet.

items.title: Cajun Popcorn Chicken Salad
items.description: Cajun Popcorn Chicken Salad is an organic cabbage mix. This salad is tossed with popcorn chicken, tomatoes, corns, black olives, nachos, island dressing, and strawberries. This salad is ideal for chicken lovers.

items.title: French Calamari Green Salad
items.description: French Calamari Green Salad is a salad tossed with tomato, beets, calamari, and lemon ranch dressing. This salad is great for sea-food lovers.

items.title: Grilled Chicken Romaine Salad
items.description: Grilled Chicken Romaine Salad is served with whole romaine lettuces with a side of grilled Chicken. The romaine lettuces are drizzled with Italian Caesar dressing and topped off with fresh red onions, corn, potatoes, and bleu cheese. This salad is perfect for dieters.

items.title: Grilled Salmon Mix Green Salad
items.description: Grilled Salmon Mix Green Salad is the new star on the Iota menu. This salad is mixed with mangoes, onions, green beans, and horse radish dressing. Freshly grilled salmon is served on top of this delightful plate.

items.title: Herb Marinated Tuna Salad
items.description: Herb Marinated Tuna is a fresh green salad that features fresh tuna marinated in herbs, mashed potato, and green beans. This salad is topped off with a drizzle of spicy oriental dressing.

items.title: Pocket Avacado Tuna Salad
items.description: Pocket Avocado Tuna is a new star on the menu. It features fresh tuna folded in guacamole, and is served in a cute avocado shell.

items.title: Soft Tofu Salad
items.description: Soft Tofu Salad is a spring mix salad tossed with onions, organic pepper, cherry tomatoes, and is finished off with a drizzle of oriental dressing.

items.title: Ultimate Dome Salad
items.description: Ultimate Dome Salad is our best seller in the salad category. This delicious salad is served with fresh tomatoes, jalapenos, pickles, crispy bacon bits, sour cream, and bleu cheese. This salad will not fail a hungry customer.

items.title: BBQ Green Chicken Pizza
items.description: BBQ Green Chicken Pizza is our most famous pizza at Iota. This pizza is topped with grilled chicken, diced pineapple, onions, cilantro, mushroom, and drizzled in tangy BBQ sauce.

items.title: Combination Bulgogi Pizza
items.description: Combination Bulgogi Pizza is a Korean style pizza that consists of bulgogi, vegetables, spices, meat sauce, and jalapeños. This pizza will surely please anyone.

items.title: Frutti di Mare Gorgonzola Cheese Pasta
items.description: Frutti Di Mare Gorgonzola Cheese Pasta is a new pasta on Iota’s menu. The pasta consists of seafood, vegetables, and apricot.

items.title: Kimchi Carbonara
items.description: Kimchi Carbonara is Iota’s most popular pasta dish. It is a cream pasta consisted of kimchi, bacon, and mushrooms.

items.title: Pomodoro Italian Sausage Pasta
items.description: Pomodoro Italian Sausage Pasta is an italian style pasta. This pasta has juicy italian sausage, onions, tomatoes, chili, and is spiced with paprika.

items.title: Shrimp Alfredo Pasta
items.description: Shrimp Alfredo is a pasta that consists of shrimp, parmesan cheese, onions, and creamy sauce. Definitely a dish to try.

items.title: Sweet Pumpkin With Spicy Shrimp Salad Pizza
items.description: Sweet Pumpkin with Spicy Shrimp Salad Pizza is a sweet and spicy pizza. This pizza has  interesting toppings such as fresh sweet pumpkin, cajun marinated shrimp, salad, onion, chili, and is spiced with paprika.

items.title: Double Double Cheese Burger
items.description: Double Double Cheese Burger is a delicious hamburger that satisfies anyone. It has double the ground beef patties, and comes with tomato, cabbage, and swiss cheese.
